## 🔌 4. Integrated Third-Party Services

1. **EmailJS (`@emailjs/browser`)**: Configured on the client-side to directly dispatch verification confirmation emails to customers who verify their tickets.
2. **WhatsApp Links**: Provides quick-action links `https://wa.me/{number}?text={message}` (with configurable phone numbers and prefilled text queries) to bridge buyers to agents for transactional finalization.
3. **AWS S3 / Forge Storage**: Handled in [server/storage.ts](file:///c:/Users/USER/Desktop/School/fifa/server/storage.ts) for uploading match graphics or related attachments to S3 via presigned PUT requests.
4. **Google Maps Proxy**: Handled in [client/src/components/Map.tsx](file:///c:/Users/USER/Desktop/School/fifa/client/src/components/Map.tsx) for displaying map coordinates of stadium venues.

